description: Data Model Baselines for exporting the data from Splunk to ArcSight CEF

if(isstr(cef_cs5Label) AND isstr(cef_cs5), cef_cs5Label, case(hasDefaultValue=1 OR isstr(cef_cs5), "unknown"))
if(isstr(cef_cs5Label) AND isstr(cef_cs5), cef_cs5Label, case(hasDefaultValue=1 OR isstr(cef_cs5), "unknown"))

if(isnum(cef_dpt) AND (cef_dpt>=0 AND cef_dpt<=65535), cef_dpt, case(hasDefaultValue=1, 0))
if(isstr(cef_flexDate1Label) AND isstr(cef_flexDate1), cef_flexDate1Label, case(hasDefaultValue=1 OR isstr(cef_flexDate1), "unknown"))
if(isstr(cef_flexNumber1Label) AND isnum(cef_flexNumber1), cef_flexNumber1Label, case(hasDefaultValue=1 OR isnum(cef_flexNumber1), "unknown"))
